data.description: Wow! 61.5 Acres, 200 Railroad Tie fence posts, cross fence ready for livestock, livestock well with windmill, two primary bedrooms with full bath, open floor concept, kitchen with breakfast nook and island, private dinning room, four bedrooms and four and a half baths. Heated Floors, over 4900 total square feet. Full unfinished walk-out basement, plumbed for another bath. 60x40 heated shop/barn with another unfinished bath. Large 55x20 walk-in chicken coop. Two car attached garage with 13.5 foor ceilings, loading ramp, 35 trees planted this year. Easy highway access + VIEWS!!! 20 minutes from Town, Property runs along the highway and the wild life- deer, antelope, turkeys!!!
